@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title List Command Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant ListCommand
participant RecordList
participant Ui
participant Storage

User -> Resumake: list [TYPE]
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: ListCommand
Resumake -> ListCommand: execute(list)
ListCommand -> RecordList: iterate records
ListCommand -> Ui: print matching records
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare
alt no content change
    Storage -> Storage: skip write
else changed
    Storage -> Storage: write file
end
@enduml
